00:02:57,888 --> 00:02:58,989
[SPEAKER_01]: Cambridge in November.

31
00:02:59,009 --> 00:03:00,831
[SPEAKER_01]: It was cold.

32
00:03:00,871 --> 00:03:03,253
[SPEAKER_01]: So I think I'll find one over the summer that I like.

33
00:03:04,254 --> 00:03:05,015
[SPEAKER_01]: I'm a pet lover.

34
00:03:05,035 --> 00:03:10,881
[SPEAKER_01]: I had my first dog gifted to us, my children and I, from my husband.

35
00:03:10,921 --> 00:03:13,963
[SPEAKER_01]: I say it's the best present he's ever given us.

36
00:03:14,824 --> 00:03:18,187
