55
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:37,821
[SPEAKER_00]: That's for sure.

56
00:04:37,841 --> 00:04:39,101
[SPEAKER_00]: It keeps me out of trouble.

57
00:04:39,381 --> 00:04:40,522
[SPEAKER_00]: Yes Yeah, there you go.

58
00:04:40,942 --> 00:04:42,182
