[SPEAKER_01]: Well, first of all, I'm very proud to be the 36th person to be on your show.

70
00:05:20,292 --> 00:05:21,313
[SPEAKER_00]: Thank you.

71
00:05:21,713 --> 00:05:22,754
[SPEAKER_00]: We love the plug.

72
