[SPEAKER_01]: The city residents, volunteers, and the team at City Hall and beyond.

77
00:05:40,130 --> 00:05:50,618
[SPEAKER_01]: So I think the first biggest accomplishment was setting, changing the way we hire in the city of Medford and really hiring candidates that are

78
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:55,563
