[SPEAKER_01]: The Clippership Connector was a huge accomplishment.

85
00:06:29,515 --> 00:06:41,100
[SPEAKER_01]: Car Park is fully opening the end of the year, but we've done basketball courts over and tennis courts over and tree projects throughout our parks and throughout our community.

86
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:48,864
[SPEAKER_01]: So setting goals like let's plant 200 trees this year and we put it on the team and we seem to get it done.

87
