110
00:09:11,447 --> 00:09:16,091
[SPEAKER_01]: We've also spent millions in updates to our fire stations.

111
00:09:16,331 --> 00:09:22,655
[SPEAKER_01]: I'm sure there's millions more to go, but we've spent millions on windows, on roofs, and the list goes on.

112
00:09:22,735 --> 00:09:26,138
[SPEAKER_01]: Kitchens, we've rehabbed kitchens, so my chief of staff is really

113
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:31,325
[SPEAKER_01]: taken the lead on that with our facilities director and the team at the fire station.

114
00:09:33,967 --> 00:09:37,631
[SPEAKER_01]: Building a sense of accountability in this city, too, is a big accomplishment for me.

115
00:09:37,652 --> 00:09:39,133
[SPEAKER_01]: It didn't come easy.

116
00:09:39,153 --> 00:09:47,382
[SPEAKER_01]: There was no human resources in Medford when I first started, so to have a very strong human resource director that is helping to

117
00:09:48,283 --> 00:09:54,007
