234
00:19:15,823 --> 00:19:33,392
[SPEAKER_01]: It wasn't until, and I thought everything was going smoothly until Salem Street kind of hit the fan, and then that's when I started, I need more information, I need to know what's going on, why is everybody so upset, because I feel like one of my major roles is to keep people calm and in touch with the communications piece.

235
