[SPEAKER_01]: There's a petition of over 700 people.

238
00:19:39,900 --> 00:19:44,587
[SPEAKER_01]: I know that's going on at the same time another quarter is going on.

239
00:19:44,607 --> 00:19:45,668
[SPEAKER_01]: I feel like this is too fast.

240
00:19:45,998 --> 00:19:51,622
[SPEAKER_01]: you know, too fast, and then some of our employees were getting attacked on social media.

241
00:19:51,682 --> 00:19:54,704
[SPEAKER_01]: So that's the point where I said, I need to get involved here.

242
