[SPEAKER_01]: And I listened, and I assumed what I was hearing was accurate.

244
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:11,715
[SPEAKER_01]: And then it wasn't until we really got to the residential where I said, oh my gosh, nobody, like I saw the,

