375
00:31:02,252 --> 00:31:17,435
[SPEAKER_01]: continue to know that they're very welcome here in Medford and it's a place that is helping people and You know, I see a positive wonderful City that is thriving on many many levels Vibrant vibrant.

376
00:31:17,475 --> 00:31:26,457
[SPEAKER_01]: Yes, and we are working on it and yeah, yep and I say we because there's just so many people who maybe don't agree on every single thing, but

